'''The Clash''' were an [[England|English]] [[punk rock]] band, active from 1976 to 1986, part of the original wave of UK [[Punk subculture|punk]].<ref name="Gilbert-Pasion_Is_a_Fashion">{{cite book 
 | last = Gilbert 
 | first = Pat 
