 | last = Deeth
 | first = John
 | publisher = jdeeth.home.mchsi.com 
}}</ref>  In early September,  Levene was kicked out for never showing up to practice.<ref name="Westway_to_the_World" /> On [[September 21]], [[1976]] the band performed at the [[100 Club Punk Festival]], sharing the bill with the Sex Pistols, [[Siouxsie and the Banshees]] and [[Subway Sect]].<ref name="Gray-Last_Gang_in_Town" /><ref>{{cite web 
